7. Gameplay Tag Examples

Recommended tag names:

Player.Health
Player.Stamina
Weapon.CurrentAmmo
Weapon.RuntimeData
Input.Action.Move
Input.Action.MouseLocation
AI.TargetActor
Quest.ActiveObjective

A good naming style is:

System.Category.Name

Examples:

Player.Stat.Health
Weapon.Data.CurrentAmmo
Input.Action.MouseLocation
AI.Target.CurrentActor


